[This case is quite distant from the locale of the previous cases in
April 2011 in San Juan province. The tests used to confirm this case
as a St. Louis encephalitis virus infection are not specified. ProMED
would be interested in receiving information about the suspected, but
not confirmed, cases as it becomes available.

A HealthMap/ProMED interactive map showing the location of Corrientes
province in Argentina can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/0X08
